sequenceDiagram
    autonumber

    box Client
        participant C as MCP client
    end

    box Server
        participant MCP as MCP control plane
        participant HTTP as HTTP data plane
    end

    Note over C,HTTP: (a) Client-driven — 2 MCP round trips

    rect rgb(255, 236, 236)
        Note over C,MCP: MCP RTT 1 — hints
        C->>MCP: request format hints
        MCP-->>C: size hints per encoding
        C->>C: select format locally
    end

    rect rgb(255, 236, 236)
        Note over C,HTTP: MCP RTT 2 — delivery
        C->>MCP: fetch chosen format
        alt small result
            MCP-->>C: inline JSON
        else large columnar result
            MCP-->>C: descriptor + URL
            C->>HTTP: GET bytes
            HTTP-->>C: Parquet / Arrow
        end
    end
